title: The Alien Council - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 9/23/22

description:
Guest host Connie Willis and open lines callers ask psychic medium Vincent Genna questions about his interactions with aliens from other dimensions, what the purpose is of their visits to Earth, and if they will be able to help humans reach a state of higher consciousness.
